{"tid":2188781,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【細So桃色風波】疑似小四不雅片流出    ViuTV音樂節目《Show Time我主場》張紫語認係女主角","createTime":"2020-09-04T12:34:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T16:12:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f8f623a31065bbf4bcde62016057e9b768688499","tid":2188781,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:34:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NRMuxPz7kXiHmjos2Dzi.Q--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTU3/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-09/6d48eb40-ee93-11ea-9bbb-a0e6ef92872d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FNRMuxPz7kXiHmjos2Dzi.Q--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTU3%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-09%2F6d48eb40-ee93-11ea-9bbb-a0e6ef92872d&h=d4f9ff69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被爆出背妻偷食嘅前DJ蘇耀宗（細So），負面新聞冇停過，除爆出偷食人妻網紅練美施（Macy），Macy更自稱曾染上性病，之後Macy仲爆出其實細So同另一個女子有染，即有傳係同樣係人妻、曾參加ViuTV音樂節目《Show Time我主場》嘅張紫語（Jelly）有關。<br />\n<br />\n今日網上流出幾段疑似Jelly嘅不雅短片，開頭見嗰位女子着住小背心，對住鏡頭摸胸，及後又見到該名女子脫去上衣，裸露上身，重點拍攝其重要部位，意識非常大膽。比對張紫語跟片中女子心口粒痣，位置巧合相同，引來唔少網民熱議。<br />\n<br />\n張紫語今日喺IG動態留言，佢認自己係片中女主角，不過佢強調同細So冇性關係！<br />\n<br />\n佢喺社交網限時動態更發聲明：<br />\n<br />\n多謝各界朋友的關心，我有以下幾點回應<br />\n<br />\n1）我和男事主早在唱歌比賽之前就已經認識多年，一直都是朋友關係，我們多年來只有在工作上同場過，所以我絕對不是女事主口中所講的主角，更從來沒有跟男事主互傳過短片甚至發生關係，懇請大家不要再胡亂猜測。<br />\n<br />\n2）至於網上正在流傳的短片，其實是我於六、七年前發給當時長期身在異地工作的丈夫，屬於我們夫妻之間的事。另外，我早已在數年前就收到過來自陌生人的訊息，他們當時也是利用現正流傳的同一批短片來恐嚇和勒索我，我當刻已經即時報警處理，警方亦有立案調查了一段很長的時間，已證實是黑客所為。<br />\n<br />\n3）對於所有記者和傳媒朋友的提問，一律不會再回應了，並以此聲明作準。辛苦晒！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DZkD.qpkPjxbMdP1z5ipcQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-09/8650d8f0-ee93-11ea-bddd-8a1e3edfdad6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FDZkD.qpkPjxbMdP1z5ipcQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-09%2F8650d8f0-ee93-11ea-bddd-8a1e3edfdad6&h=64f8a3df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bvlWZk5qVtyhJRwbEed_ug--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-09/9e198fe0-ee93-11ea-b5b6-dc4bda3d483e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FbvlWZk5qVtyhJRwbEed_ug--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-09%2F9e198fe0-ee93-11ea-b5b6-dc4bda3d483e&h=01860fd6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d5a54628a06430094521f4a9099694a2b3a5a05","tid":2188781,"uid":201182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:51:29.000Z","msg":"好似差咁d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4d001b5bac9be9f3696d06212a453a25271450","tid":2188781,"uid":294648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T13:05:37.000Z","msg":"Show Lin 我主場<br />\n<br />\n片呢?"},{"pid":"7eaa5e517d3ccc8139cfbfccd72d4e2d92863b16","tid":2188781,"uid":228223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T13:54:15.000Z","msg":"片 or 伯母，自己識do啦！"},{"pid":"a245a65fcb4492b82ea6b8027095a5c557135e2c","tid":2188781,"uid":271485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T16:12:21.000Z","msg":"又黑客呀？<br />\nkeith leung無叫雞"}]}